SELECT Users.name, Meals.meal_date FROM Users INNER JOIN UserMeals ON Users.id = UserMeals.user_id INNER JOIN Meals ON UserMeals.meal_id = Meals.id WHERE Users.age > 30 AND Meals.total_calories < 800 ORDER BY Users.name ASC;

SELECT Users.name, SUM(Meals.total_calories) AS total_calories_consumed FROM Users INNER JOIN UserMeals ON Users.id = UserMeals.user_id INNER JOIN Meals ON UserMeals.meal_id = Meals.id GROUP BY Users.name HAVING total_calories_consumed > 1500 ORDER BY total_calories_consumed DESC;

SELECT Users.name, Meals.meal_date, FoodItems.name, FoodItems.calories FROM Users INNER JOIN UserMeals ON Users.id = UserMeals.user_id INNER JOIN Meals ON UserMeals.meal_id = Meals.id INNER JOIN FoodItems ON Meals.id = FoodItems.id WHERE Users.age < 50 ORDER BY Users.name, Meals.meal_date ASC LIMIT 10;
